    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《花奴令》是一款无需联网的纯单机游戏。</strong>出于共同的爱好，我们尝试采用了经典<strong>纯爱GALGAME的风格与玩法，</strong>三GE、多BE、还有一条男主带上两只猫咪神隐的TE线需要手动挖掘...游戏特邀多位编剧、摄影、声优与音乐人以<strong>不署名的方式友情创作，</strong>内含近200张高清CG照片、5套服装、5种相机及隐藏音频可供收藏。<strong>适合断网或静夜独享，希望大家喜欢，另有VR模式将在后续更新！</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>请各位花友加入官方群.每周抽取游戏Cdkey与主演签名照哦！</u></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    官方1群： 690882636   BUG反馈群：697845221 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· <strong>邂逅两位小花奴和她的朋友们</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/84ceb2fcd36d7d4ef024c3ac13a9d502.avif?t=1743654591\" width=600 height=200 /></span>【桃子】中华田园狸花喵，相当于人类18岁。元气单纯、耿直忠诚，一口猫粮跟你一辈子。 <br>【云朵】布偶喵，相当于人类19岁。温柔敏感、喵中御姐，美丽只是她最不值得一提的优点。      <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/97fa8cf3399548932220937daf7bc551.avif?t=1743654591\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【芝芝】金吉拉喵，相当于人类19岁。傲娇难哄，想要讨好她可不容易。 <br>【莓莓】短腿起司喵，相当于人类18岁。呆萌可爱，又菜又爱玩。<br>【露娜】品种未知，年龄未知。甜美可人，身世神秘的花奴镇守门人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>·  特色一  体验和小花奴的甜蜜日常，收集近200张高清CG！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/e1bcba46db7033f2b7989e981b8c9588.poster.avif?t=1743654591\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/e1bcba46db7033f2b7989e981b8c9588.webm?t=1743654591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/e1bcba46db7033f2b7989e981b8c9588.mp4?t=1743654591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >·  <strong>特色二  用相机记录与小花奴相处瞬间，收集迥然不同的拍照效果（后果）！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/e71eedeec770a92c39754145c8cd9945.poster.avif?t=1743654591\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/e71eedeec770a92c39754145c8cd9945.webm?t=1743654591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/e71eedeec770a92c39754145c8cd9945.mp4?t=1743654591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >·  <strong>特色三  通关解锁特别篇.花奴摄影棚，收集4位猫娘、5套服装与6只独特相机滤镜！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/7be79b50cfbbfd273af1af99a5909a03.poster.avif?t=1743654591\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/7be79b50cfbbfd273af1af99a5909a03.webm?t=1743654591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/7be79b50cfbbfd273af1af99a5909a03.mp4?t=1743654591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>·  特色四  受玩家选择影响的多分支结局，收集3个GE、1个TE、14种不同BE（死法）！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/34523f83877a2f3835c40487a398d55a.poster.avif?t=1743654591\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/34523f83877a2f3835c40487a398d55a.webm?t=1743654591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196550/extras/34523f83877a2f3835c40487a398d55a.mp4?t=1743654591\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >·  <strong>关于我们</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   我们是一家由5位志同道合的游戏爱好者组成的独立游戏工作室。这个小游戏是我们的第一部作品，自2022年11月开始第一支样片拍摄，历经2年的摄制与研发，数易其稿，希望大家喜欢。我们当中，有的进过大厂、有的遭遇裁员、有的做过动漫、有的送过外卖...但最终，很幸运，我们走到了这里。也许我们只是一群过气的古惑仔，但我们热爱游戏，永远是少年。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   桃花庵主唐伯虎有诗云，“春来三月香风送, 便是花奴问君安”，想必诗人一定也得到过猫猫的安慰。在此，要特别感谢所有帮助过我们的朋友家人，以及露娜和她的替身哈娜两只小喵，游戏做完，她们也都长大了。愿我们的小花奴能够给大家送去温暖与陪伴。最后，为大家呈上一点小福利，恳请各位客官多多支持，让我们有机会把这个故事续写下去。<u>#在游戏主界面回车输入“花奴”的完整拼音，即可在摄影棚解锁全套汉服视频与照片：）</u></p>",
